Write a query to find the top 3 most ordered products along with the total quantity ordered.


Products
-------------------------
| product_id (INT) | name |
-------------------------
|        1         |  A   |
|        2         |  B   |
|        3         |  C   |
|        4         |  D   |
-------------------------

Orders
---------------------------------
| order_id (INT) | product_id |
---------------------------------
|       1       |      1     |
|       2       |      2     |
|       3       |      1     |
|       4       |      3     |
|       5       |      2     |
|       6       |      3     |
|       7       |      3     |



SELECT p.product_id,p.name,COUNT(os.order_id) as Total_Quantity_ordered
FROM orderss os
JOIN products p
ON os.product_id = p.product_id
GROUP BY p.product_id,p.name
